WEBVTT


00:01:27.079 --> 00:01:27.400
No, wait.

00:01:27.400 --> 00:01:28.879
What's wrong with you three?

00:01:29.000 --> 00:01:30.560
You usually fight so fiercely.

00:01:30.920 --> 00:01:31.959
But when something bad happens,

00:01:31.959 --> 00:01:33.480
you suddenly join forces.

00:01:33.519 --> 00:01:34.319
I've said it before.

00:01:34.319 --> 00:01:35.719
If you want to scam me, I'll let you.

00:01:35.920 --> 00:01:37.280
If you want to trick me, I'll let you.

00:01:37.400 --> 00:01:38.200
Anyway,

00:01:38.280 --> 00:01:39.280
I'm sticking with you.

00:01:40.319 --> 00:01:41.799
I've even accepted the daughter-in-law bracelet.

00:01:41.799 --> 00:01:42.920
Why still draw a line between us?

00:01:43.359 --> 00:01:44.000
Chengwen,

00:01:44.000 --> 00:01:45.560
I believe in your intelligence.

00:01:45.719 --> 00:01:47.120
You must be planning something big.

00:01:47.519 --> 00:01:48.879
Just go for it.

00:01:49.000 --> 00:01:50.680
What big game am I playing?

00:01:51.000 --> 00:01:52.680
I'm just squandering money!

00:01:52.879 --> 00:01:54.120
Why are you guys egging me on?

00:01:54.120 --> 00:01:55.120
Let's see how you explain this

00:01:55.120 --> 00:01:56.079
to your families when you get back!

00:01:56.120 --> 00:01:57.120
You're yelling at me.

00:01:58.920 --> 00:02:00.319
What are you doing?

00:02:02.599 --> 00:02:03.319
Chengwen,

00:02:03.319 --> 00:02:04.680
don't feel too much pressure.

00:02:06.680 --> 00:02:08.199
I'm the CEO of Qianfeng.

00:02:08.280 --> 00:02:09.319
As for the project,

00:02:09.400 --> 00:02:10.520
I have my own judgment.

00:02:11.159 --> 00:02:12.479
You don't need to worry about it.

00:02:12.919 --> 00:02:13.840
You're all stupid.

00:02:13.840 --> 00:02:14.479
Stupid women.

00:02:14.599 --> 00:02:15.879
You three stupid women.

00:02:16.719 --> 00:02:18.319
Why are they all so good to me?

00:02:18.719 --> 00:02:20.199
You just realized we're good?

00:02:24.000 --> 00:02:26.560
How is this any different from running naked?

00:02:31.360 --> 00:02:32.919
I've already negotiated with them.

00:02:33.319 --> 00:02:35.479
Now we just need to sign the contract and pay.

00:02:35.599 --> 00:02:36.919
That piece of land

00:02:36.919 --> 00:02:38.080
will be yours.

00:02:38.599 --> 00:02:39.719
Good, good, good.

00:02:39.919 --> 00:02:41.319
With this piece of land,

00:02:41.560 --> 00:02:42.759
our Leng family

00:02:42.759 --> 00:02:44.280
will be fully revitalized.

00:02:44.319 --> 00:02:45.599
When I was stranded in Haicheng,

00:02:46.280 --> 00:02:47.599
I was kindly taken in by Miss Leng.

00:02:47.759 --> 00:02:48.639
Now,

00:02:48.639 --> 00:02:50.680
I'm just returning the favor.

00:02:51.319 --> 00:02:53.280
Hehehe.

00:02:54.599 --> 00:02:55.360
Chairman!

00:02:55.360 --> 00:02:56.759
Bad news! Bad news!

00:02:57.080 --> 00:02:58.960
At the Haicheng City Hall meeting,

00:02:58.960 --> 00:02:59.800
Miss Leng made a decision on the spot

00:02:59.919 --> 00:03:01.000
to follow Lu Chengwen

00:03:01.000 --> 00:03:02.879
and invest in the Chengnan construction project!

00:03:03.080 --> 00:03:04.520
The contract was signed right there!

00:03:05.000 --> 00:03:05.919
What did you say?

00:03:08.360 --> 00:03:09.599
How much is the investment?

00:03:09.759 --> 00:03:10.560
Five billion.

00:03:10.960 --> 00:03:12.080
The Xu family invested ten billion.

00:03:12.199 --> 00:03:13.120
The Chen family invested even more,

00:03:13.159 --> 00:03:13.960
twenty billion!

00:03:15.759 --> 00:03:16.560
Mr. Leng,

00:03:17.400 --> 00:03:18.199
what's wrong?

00:03:18.199 --> 00:03:19.919
This is Qianfeng's

00:03:19.919 --> 00:03:22.680
last bit of liquid capital!

00:03:28.960 --> 00:03:30.120
Lu Chengwen!

00:03:39.520 --> 00:03:40.319
Young Master.

00:03:41.719 --> 00:03:42.919
Did the Leng family back out?

00:03:43.280 --> 00:03:44.080
No.

00:03:44.560 --> 00:03:46.080
But your expression...

00:03:46.080 --> 00:03:47.080
It's very solemn.

00:03:47.680 --> 00:03:48.520
Lu Chengwen.

00:03:49.960 --> 00:03:52.719
He tricked Leng Qingqiu to invest in the South City project.

00:03:52.719 --> 00:03:54.120
Now all of the Leng family's liquid funds

00:03:54.120 --> 00:03:55.080
have been depleted.

00:03:55.360 --> 00:03:56.520
Besides them,

00:03:56.879 --> 00:03:57.599
the Xu family

00:03:57.599 --> 00:03:58.199
and the Chen family

00:03:58.199 --> 00:03:59.560
are all going to fall into this trap.

00:04:00.280 --> 00:04:01.520
I don't know if Lu Chengwen

00:04:01.520 --> 00:04:03.400
is trying to use this opportunity

00:04:03.439 --> 00:04:04.280
to annex Haicheng.

00:04:04.360 --> 00:04:05.159
What?

00:04:05.599 --> 00:04:06.400
Young Master,

00:04:06.400 --> 00:04:07.479
I'll go kill him.

00:04:07.680 --> 00:04:08.479
Not yet.

00:04:09.280 --> 00:04:10.719
If it comes to the worst,

00:04:11.000 --> 00:04:12.719
I will handle it myself.

00:04:13.280 --> 00:04:14.080
Right now,

00:04:14.080 --> 00:04:16.720
there's still room to maneuver.

00:04:21.920 --> 00:04:23.480
King Tietuo greets the Master.

00:04:24.079 --> 00:04:24.759
The Young Master

00:04:24.759 --> 00:04:26.680
has met some resistance in Haicheng.

00:04:26.879 --> 00:04:27.600
You go

00:04:27.600 --> 00:04:28.920
and lend him a hand.

00:04:29.079 --> 00:04:29.879
Yes.

00:04:38.519 --> 00:04:39.319
Dad,

00:04:39.759 --> 00:04:41.000
the new plan for the South City project,

00:04:41.000 --> 00:04:41.920
you've seen it, right?

00:04:42.000 --> 00:04:42.920
If it succeeds,

00:04:43.079 --> 00:04:44.519
it's the perfect opportunity for our Leng family

00:04:44.519 --> 00:04:45.519
to return to the top.

00:04:45.560 --> 00:04:46.360
Enough!

00:04:46.600 --> 00:04:48.120
You're still stubbornly obsessed!

00:04:48.279 --> 00:04:49.079
In three days,

00:04:49.480 --> 00:04:51.720
I will reappoint Gu Zhantian

00:04:51.800 --> 00:04:53.720
as the CEO of our Qianfeng Group.

00:04:53.920 --> 00:04:55.279
Do you even know his background?

00:04:55.360 --> 00:04:56.399
How can you trust him so easily?

00:04:56.720 --> 00:04:57.519
Qingqiu,

00:04:57.920 --> 00:04:59.560
I'll give you one more chance.

00:04:59.759 --> 00:05:00.800
Within three days,

00:05:01.199 --> 00:05:03.680
you make Lu Chengwen return that five billion.

00:05:03.759 --> 00:05:04.879
I'll let bygones be bygones.

00:05:05.720 --> 00:05:06.519
Otherwise,

00:05:06.519 --> 00:05:07.959
you can get the hell out of Qianfeng!

00:05:08.519 --> 00:05:09.399
From then on,

00:05:09.399 --> 00:05:10.720
don't even think about touching the business again.

00:05:17.519 --> 00:05:18.319
You...

00:05:33.720 --> 00:05:34.519
Fired?

00:05:35.680 --> 00:05:36.480
Uncle Leng,

00:05:36.680 --> 00:05:38.120
Qingqiu has worked so hard all these years

00:05:38.160 --> 00:05:39.800
just to revitalize Qianfeng Group.

00:05:40.120 --> 00:05:40.879
By doing this,

00:05:40.879 --> 00:05:42.279
aren't you just abandoning her?

00:05:42.399 --> 00:05:43.519
You are her father!

00:05:43.720 --> 00:05:45.279
And you're her fiance!

00:05:45.600 --> 00:05:46.959
Didn't you abandon her just the same?

00:05:47.000 --> 00:05:47.800
Uncle Leng,

00:05:48.279 --> 00:05:49.759
what Qingqiu needs most right now

00:05:49.759 --> 00:05:51.519
is your support and understanding.

00:05:51.800 --> 00:05:52.480
Whatever you do,

00:05:52.480 --> 00:05:53.920
you never consider Qingqiu's feelings!

00:05:54.199 --> 00:05:55.680
It's like this with company decisions,

00:05:55.920 --> 00:05:56.920
and it's like this with the marriage alliance.

00:05:57.079 --> 00:05:59.120
By doing this, you've stripped away her dreams.

00:05:59.120 --> 00:06:00.279
Do you even deserve to be her father?

00:06:02.920 --> 00:06:04.720
You want to stand up for her, right?

00:06:05.120 --> 00:06:07.120
Then why don't you pay that five billion for her?

00:06:07.199 --> 00:06:08.360
Isn't it just five billion?

00:06:08.480 --> 00:06:09.160
I'll pay it!

00:06:09.160 --> 00:06:10.279
I see that in your eyes, besides money,

00:06:10.279 --> 00:06:11.199
there's nothing else.

00:06:11.959 --> 00:06:12.759
Shihan,

00:06:13.480 --> 00:06:14.720
immediately transfer to Qianfeng Group's account

00:06:14.720 --> 00:06:15.600
five billion.

00:06:15.879 --> 00:06:16.519
Mr. Lu,

00:06:16.519 --> 00:06:17.399
don't be impulsive.

00:06:17.680 --> 00:06:18.920
I told you to go, so go!

00:06:19.319 --> 00:06:20.879
It must be in the account within 15 minutes.

00:06:21.120 --> 00:06:21.920
Go now!

00:06:22.120 --> 00:06:22.920
Yes.

00:06:24.519 --> 00:06:25.279
Uncle Leng,

00:06:25.360 --> 00:06:26.519
are you satisfied now?

00:06:26.800 --> 00:06:27.680
Can Qingqiu's position as CEO

00:06:27.680 --> 00:06:28.680
be secured now?

00:06:29.120 --> 00:06:30.519
It's secured for now.

00:06:32.519 --> 00:06:33.480
Secured?

00:06:46.920 --> 00:06:47.720
Shihan,

00:06:47.759 --> 00:06:48.680
transfer that five billion directly

00:06:48.680 --> 00:06:50.600
to Leng Qingqiu's personal account!

00:06:58.959 --> 00:07:00.399
Leng Tianhao, oh Leng Tianhao,

00:07:00.519 --> 00:07:01.319
let's see how you

00:07:01.319 --> 00:07:02.879
kick Leng Qingqiu aside now.

00:07:05.120 --> 00:07:05.920
Brother Chengwen!

00:07:26.959 --> 00:07:27.759
Qingqiu

00:07:28.480 --> 00:07:29.319
What are you doing?

00:07:30.920 --> 00:07:32.959
Even though you didn't answer me last time,

00:07:33.959 --> 00:07:35.120
but

00:07:35.120 --> 00:07:37.120
I already understand how you feel.

00:07:39.199 --> 00:07:40.000
No,

00:07:40.560 --> 00:07:42.079
you should just...

00:07:42.079 --> 00:07:43.360
calm down a bit.

00:07:47.920 --> 00:07:49.680
Darn it, this woman...

00:07:49.720 --> 00:07:50.920
really makes me want to...

00:07:52.920 --> 00:07:53.480
Right, right, right.

00:07:53.480 --> 00:07:54.120
No way.

00:07:54.120 --> 00:07:54.920
Stop.

00:07:55.279 --> 00:07:56.480
I can't let my mind wander.

00:08:02.759 --> 00:08:05.279
What I told you last time was all true.

00:08:05.560 --> 00:08:06.920
I like you.

00:08:08.000 --> 00:08:09.680
I truly mean it.

00:08:16.199 --> 00:08:17.000
Qingqiu,

00:08:17.120 --> 00:08:18.279
well,

00:08:18.279 --> 00:08:19.120
actually...

00:08:59.559 --> 00:09:00.360
Anyway,

00:09:00.399 --> 00:09:01.519
you don't need to say anymore.

00:09:01.519 --> 00:09:02.759
I will prove it to you.

00:09:03.399 --> 00:09:04.200
Also,

00:09:04.200 --> 00:09:05.200
about those five billion,

00:09:05.200 --> 00:09:06.759
just consider it a loan.

00:09:06.799 --> 00:09:08.159
I will definitely pay you back.

00:09:09.919 --> 00:09:10.240
Then,

00:09:10.519 --> 00:09:11.519
I'll be leaving now.

00:09:20.399 --> 00:09:21.360
Brother Chengwen,

00:09:21.519 --> 00:09:23.200
I've been kicked out of my house.

00:09:23.200 --> 00:09:24.679
You have to take responsibility for me.

00:09:25.080 --> 00:09:26.200
I'll wait for you at the bar.

00:09:26.200 --> 00:09:27.000
I sent you the address.

00:09:27.120 --> 00:09:27.919
Come quickly.

00:09:33.480 --> 00:09:34.480
Isn't this...

00:09:36.279 --> 00:09:37.919
Will this ever end?

00:09:59.120 --> 00:09:59.919
Leng Qingqiu,

00:10:00.480 --> 00:10:01.919
you're quite capable.

00:10:02.080 --> 00:10:03.799
Getting Lu Chengwen to scheme against me.

00:10:03.799 --> 00:10:05.600
You think just because he transferred five billion to you,

00:10:05.600 --> 00:10:07.000
I can't do anything about you?

00:10:07.159 --> 00:10:08.559
Let me tell you the truth.

00:10:09.000 --> 00:10:09.720
Zhantian

00:10:09.720 --> 00:10:12.080
has already contacted a major consortium for me.

00:10:12.519 --> 00:10:14.320
They are willing to give our Qianfeng Group

00:10:14.320 --> 00:10:15.799
a capital injection of five billion.

00:10:16.919 --> 00:10:17.600
Qingqiu,

00:10:17.600 --> 00:10:19.000
I've made an appointment with their representative.

00:10:19.080 --> 00:10:20.360
We'll sign the contract at 8 PM tonight.

00:10:20.519 --> 00:10:21.320
Let's go together.

00:10:21.720 --> 00:10:22.519
Sure.

00:10:22.960 --> 00:10:24.480
I'd really like to see

00:10:24.480 --> 00:10:26.200
what kind of tricks you're playing.

00:10:32.720 --> 00:10:33.519
Strange.

00:10:33.879 --> 00:10:34.519
Xu Xuejiao

00:10:34.519 --> 00:10:36.480
booked this bar, but why are there no customers?

00:10:37.279 --> 00:10:37.679
Young Master Lu,

00:10:37.679 --> 00:10:38.360
I'm sorry.

00:10:38.360 --> 00:10:39.559
This place is booked out today.

00:10:39.559 --> 00:10:40.559
We're not receiving guests.

00:10:40.879 --> 00:10:41.679
Ah, no.

00:10:41.720 --> 00:10:42.919
My friend asked me to come.

00:10:42.919 --> 00:10:43.679
I'm here to find her.

00:10:44.399 --> 00:10:45.320
Let go of me!

00:10:45.399 --> 00:10:46.519
Are you crazy?

00:10:47.919 --> 00:10:48.679
Young Master Lu!

00:10:49.120 --> 00:10:49.960
Let go of me!

00:10:50.480 --> 00:10:51.320
Little girl,

00:10:51.399 --> 00:10:52.519
you've got quite a temper.

00:10:52.679 --> 00:10:54.320
I like girls like you.

00:10:54.480 --> 00:10:55.320
Let go!

00:11:00.480 --> 00:11:01.399
Who are you?

00:11:01.919 --> 00:11:03.080
This place is booked out.

00:11:03.200 --> 00:11:04.000
Get lost!

00:11:07.320 --> 00:11:08.279
King Tietuo.

00:11:08.279 --> 00:11:09.320
Highly skilled in martial arts.

00:11:09.480 --> 00:11:11.360
Sent to Haicheng to support Gu Zhantian.

00:11:11.759 --> 00:11:13.360
In the future, he will become Gu Zhantian's

00:11:13.360 --> 00:11:14.080
capable general.

00:11:15.000 --> 00:11:16.480
This guy's combat power is very high.

00:11:17.000 --> 00:11:17.799
I can't afford to mess with him.

00:11:20.360 --> 00:11:21.159
Well, since

00:11:21.159 --> 00:11:22.360
you've booked this place out,

00:11:23.200 --> 00:11:24.000
I'll leave it to you.

00:11:24.080 --> 00:11:24.919
Let's go.

00:11:26.919 --> 00:11:28.480
You can get lost by yourself.

00:11:28.919 --> 00:11:29.879
She stays.